# E7 BP Helper — GitHub 仓库用途：
#   Vercel 部署 frontend/（静态站）
#   Render 部署 Flask API + TensorFlow（render.yaml）
# 不上传：本地 venv、exe 打包、爬虫/训练、个人笔记

# --- Python / local env ---
.venv/
venv/
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyo
.Python
*.egg-info/
.eggs/
pip-wheel-metadata/

# --- IDE / OS ---
.idea/
.vscode/
.cursor/
*.swp
*.swo
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# --- Runtime logs / local state ---
*.log
recommender_service_port.txt
dist_exe_out.log

# --- Frontend（Vercel 在云端 npm build，不提交构建产物）---
frontend/node_modules/
frontend/dist/
frontend/.env
frontend/.env.local
frontend/.env.*.local

# --- Windows exe 打包（本地分发用，与 Vercel/Render 无关）---
build/
dist/
*.spec
build_exe.ps1
launcher.py
requirements-packaging.txt

# --- 个人笔记 / 本地草稿 ---
近期计划.txt
小本本.md
README_SCRAPERS.md

# --- 爬虫 / 训练依赖（Render 用 requirements-recommender.txt）---
requirements-scraping.txt

# --- data: 只保留线上推理所需 ---
data/debug/
data/*.html
data/*.jsonl
data/epic7_scraper_state.json
data/*_appearances.txt
data/debug_*.json
data/order4_reco.txt
data/o8_norerank.txt

# 保留: hero_details.csv, reranker/*.csv, runtime/*.pkl
# Transformer: 只保留推理文件（Render 加载 .weights.h5）
data/transformer/*
!data/transformer/
!data/transformer/rec_model_position_warfare.weights.h5
!data/transformer/rec_variables.pkl
!data/transformer/training_report_position_warfare.json

# --- workflow_scripts: 只保留后端 import 的 4 个模块 ---
workflow_scripts/*
!workflow_scripts/
!workflow_scripts/transformer_draft_data.py
!workflow_scripts/transformer_draft_model.py
!workflow_scripts/match_history_utils.py
!workflow_scripts/build_runtime_artifacts.py

